<li><span class="anchor" id="Leslie-Russell"></span>Leslie and Russell code (1964)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-Leslie-Russell&#95;1964&#95;103-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Leslie-Russell_1964-103"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>100<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-Russell&#95;1964&#95;8-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Russell_1964-8"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>8<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-Leslie&#95;1974&#95;104-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Leslie_1974-104"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>101<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-Wightman&#95;1972&#95;100-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Wightman_1972-100"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>97<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
